(107, 'Suit', 'clothes', 'Elevate your style with our premium Slim Fit Suit, crafted from a luxurious wool blend for unparalleled comfort and durability', 500, '<p>Make a lasting impression with our Classic Slim Fit Suit, the epitome of modern elegance and sophistication. Designed with meticulous attention to detail, this suit is crafted from a high-quality wool blend, offering a soft texture and breathable comfort for all-day wear. The tailored slim fit enhances your silhouette, while the notch lapels and two-button closure provide timeless appeal.</p>\r\n<p>Available in versatile colors like Navy Blue, Charcoal Grey, and Black, this suit effortlessly adapts to any formal setting, be it weddings, corporate events, or elegant evening outings. Additional features include functional inner pockets, fully lined breathable satin interior, and precision stitching for durability.</p>\r\n<p>Choose from a wide range of sizes, or opt for our custom tailoring service to ensure the perfect fit. Pair it with a crisp shirt and polished shoes to complete your dashing look. Dry clean only for long-lasting quality.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>A short description emphasizing key features:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Fabric:</strong> High-quality wool blend for a soft feel and durability.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Fit:</strong> Tailored for a modern, slim fit.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Features:</strong> Two-button closure, notch lapels, functional inner pockets.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Occasions:</strong> Perfect for weddings, business meetings, or formal events.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><strong>3. Price</strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>500Rs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><strong>4. Color Options</str', 'f2279ba2d15f5de99c3537d7e76b70c9.png'),
(108, 'Sofa', 'furniture', 'Transform your living space with our modern and luxurious Sofa, crafted with high-density foam cushions for unmatched comfort and upholstered in premium fabric. Featuring a sturdy hardwood frame, sleek design, and versatile color options, this sofa is perfect for any home decor style.', 40000, '<p>Redefine comfort and style with our premium Sofa, designed to be the centerpiece of your living space. This sofa is meticulously crafted with a durable hardwood frame for long-lasting support and upholstered in high-quality fabric that is both soft and resistant to wear.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The cushions are filled with high-density foam, providing exceptional comfort and shape retention over time. The sleek, contemporary design features clean lines, plush armrests, and perfectly proportioned dimensions, making it a versatile addition to any home.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;Available in a range of sophisticated color options, such as Charcoal Grey, Classic Beige, and Midnight Blue, this sofa effortlessly complements modern, minimalist, or traditional decor styles.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Frame Material:</strong> Solid hardwood frame for durability.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Cushions:</strong> High-density foam for comfort and longevity.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Upholstery:</strong> Premium fabric, resistant to stains and fading.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Dimensions:</strong> 84\" L x 36\" W x 34\" H (custom sizes available).</li>\r\n<li><strong>Seating Capacity:</strong> 3-4 persons.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Care Instructions:</strong> Spot clean with a damp cloth; professional cleaning recommended for deep stains.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Perfect for family lounging, entertaining guests, or relaxing after a long day, this sofa combines functionality, comfort, and aesthetic appeal. Add it to your living room for ', 'images.jfif'),
(109, 'Samsung Galaxy', 'electronics', 'Experience cutting-edge technology with our latest smartphone, featuring a sleek design, 6.7-inch AMOLED display, 108MP triple-camera system, and a powerful 5000mAh battery. Equipped with a lightning-fast processor and 5G connectivity, it ensures seamless performance for work and play.', 150000, '<p>OLED edge-to-edge display, delivering vibrant colors and exceptional clarity for streaming, gaming, and browsing.</p>\r\n<p>Capture every moment in breathtaking detail with the advanced 108MP triple-camera system, equipped with ultra-wide, telephoto, and night mode capabilities. The 32MP front-facing camera ensures your selfies and video calls look sharp and professional.</p>\r\n<p>Powered by a state-of-the-art processor and 5G connectivity, this phone provides blazing-fast speeds and smooth multitasking for all your apps and entertainment. The 5000mAh battery with fast-charging support keeps you connected all day long, while the fingerprint sensor and facial recognition offer advanced security.</p>\r\n<p>Key Features:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Display:</strong> 6.7-inch AMOLED, 120Hz refresh rate.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Camera System:</strong> 108MP + 12MP (ultra-wide) + 10MP (telephoto); 32MP front camera.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Processor:</strong> Octa-core 3.2GHz with AI optimization.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Battery:</strong> 5000mAh, 45W fast charging, wireless charging support.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Storage Options:</strong> 128GB, 256GB, 512GB (expandable via microSD).</li>\r\n<li><strong>Operating System:</strong> Android 13 or iOS 17.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Connectivity:</strong> 5G, Wi-Fi 6, Bluetooth 5.3, USB-C.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Build:</strong> Sleek aluminum frame, Gorilla Glass protection.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Available in stylish color options like Midnight Black, Cloud White, and Ocean Blue, this ', 'images (1).jfif'),
(110, 'Wireless Headphones', 'headphones', 'Immerse yourself in crystal-clear audio with our premium wireless headphones, featuring active noise cancellation, 40-hour battery life, and Bluetooth 5.3 connectivity. Designed for comfort and durability, theyâ€™re perfect for music, calls, and gaming.', 10000, '<p>Rediscover the joy of exceptional sound with our premium wireless headphones, designed for audiophiles and casual listeners alike. Engineered for superior performance, these headphones feature advanced active noise cancellation (ANC) technology, allowing you to block out distractions and focus on your music, calls, or games.</p>\r\n<p>The 40mm dynamic drivers deliver deep bass, crisp mids, and clear highs, ensuring a rich and immersive audio experience. With Bluetooth 5.3 connectivity, you can enjoy seamless pairing, stable connections, and extended range.</p>\r\n<p>Designed for all-day comfort, the headphones boast plush memory foam ear cushions and an adjustable headband to fit every user perfectly. The durable, foldable design makes them easy to carry, while the 40-hour battery life ensures uninterrupted listening. When you&rsquo;re short on time, a quick 10-minute charge gives you up to 4 hours of playtime.</p>\r\n<p>Key Features:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Audio:</strong> 40mm dynamic drivers for high-definition sound.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Noise Cancellation:</strong> Advanced ANC for immersive listening.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Battery Life:</strong> Up to 40 hours of playtime; fast charging supported.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Connectivity:</strong> Bluetooth 5.3, with support for AAC and SBC codecs.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Microphone:</strong> Built-in mic for clear calls and voice assistant access.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Design:</strong> Foldable, lightweight, and adjustable for all-day wear.</li>\r\n<l', 'images (2).jfif'),
